  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a molcajete over medium heat.",
    "Add the onions and garlic and sauté until softened.",
    "Add the mushrooms and cook until they release their moisture.",
    "Add the carrots and potatoes and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the pork sausages and cook until browned.",
    "Add the natto, chicken broth, red wine, tomato paste, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Stir well to combine.",
    "Bring the stew to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 30 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley.",
